each with a stiffness [`k = [$k]\ \textrm{N/m}`]. The springs are unstretched when the pendulum is at
rest vertically. Determine the natural period of vibration [`\tau`] of the evil hypnotist's pendulum.

_(Note the pendulum has very small displacement, use the approximation [`\sin(\theta) = \theta`])_


